{"ok":true,"sourceId":"6915cd4a17902cc008e1c32b","inserted":10,"fragments":[{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c32d","text":"Let's use React for frontend","sender":"You","datetime":"2025-01-12T15:02:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c32e","text":"Sure, MERN will be easier","sender":"Ravi","datetime":"2025-01-12T15:03:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c32f","text":"React has a huge ecosystem for UI","sender":"Meena","datetime":"2025-01-12T15:05:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c330","text":"Backend: Node + Express seems fine","sender":"You","datetime":"2025-01-13T03:30:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c331","text":"We can deploy on Vercel or Heroku","sender":"Ravi","datetime":"2025-01-13T03:35:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c332","text":"Should we use Firebase for auth?","sender":"You","datetime":"2025-01-14T04:50:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c333","text":"Firebase is quick but locks you in","sender":"Ravi","datetime":"2025-01-14T04:52:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c334","text":"If scale grows, consider MongoDB Atlas","sender":"Meena","datetime":"2025-01-15T05:45:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c335","text":"Agreed  -  MERN it is","sender":"Ravi","datetime":"2025-02-21T10:00:00.000Z"},{"_id":"6915cd4b17902cc008e1c336","text":"Also think about CI/CD with GitHub Actions","sender":"You","datetime":"2025-02-22T10:30:00.000Z"}]}